name: Nasi Angin Meliling
address: Jl. Meliling, Meliling, Kec. Kerambitan, Kabupaten Tabanan, Bali 82161, Indonesia
review 1:
I recently tried Nasi Angin Meliling and it was absolutely delicious!

The rice was perfectly cooked and the side dishes were all flavorful and well-seasoned.

I particularly enjoyed the crispy fried chicken and the spicy sambal. The portion sizes were generous and the prices were very reasonable, making it a great option for a filling and affordable meal.

The restaurant itself is clean and cozy, and the staff members were friendly and attentive. I highly recommend Nasi Angin Meliling to anyone looking for a great Indonesian meal. Thank you to the team at Nasi Angin Meliling for such a wonderful experience!"
